{"word":"G870 - ἀφόβως - aphóbōs - af-ob'-oce - Without fear","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀφόβως</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">aphóbōs</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">af-ob'-oce</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Without fear</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adverb / வினையடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"பயமில்லாமல் - வினையடை"},{"paragraph":"without fear, boldly"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Adveb from a compound of <a href=\"#/G1 - Α - A - al'-fah/1\">G1</a> (as a negative particle) and <a href=\"#/G5401 - φόβος - phóbos - fob'-os/5401\">G5401</a>; <i>fearlessly:</i> - without fear.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G3870/3870\">G3870</a>, <a href=\"#/G3874/3874\">G3874</a>, <a href=\"#/G3875/3875\">G3875</a>, <a href=\"#/G870/870\">G870</a>"}]}